The paper deals with coded computation in distributed systems, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories in computer science. However, the focus on linear transforms and the use of coding theory techniques suggest that the paper is most likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-category. Other possible sub-categories include Distributed Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI).
